Interface IonAnnotation

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<IonAnnotation>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MonaSpectrum

    public interface IonAnnotation
extends Comparable<IonAnnotation>
    Annotation of a detected feature with a chemical structure, formula, or textual description.

      • setDatabaseVersion

        void setDatabaseVersion(@Nullable
                        String databaseVersion)
        Sets a new database version description to this annotation. Either the version of the used database if available or otherwise the date of creation. Additionally, the number of entries in the database MAY be reported in round brackets after the version in the format: {version} ({#entries} entries), for example "2011-11 (1234 entries)".
        Parameters:
        databaseVersion - a String object.
